Package nodemanager.files

This package handles file helpers, which tell how to read and write the imports and exports of Wayfinding data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractWayfindingFileHelper
    The AbstractWayfindingFileHelper class is used to serve as the base for helping read and write the various data files created by the program, and used by the Wayfinding program.
    MapFileHelper

    FileType

Package nodemanager.files Description

This package handles file helpers, which tell how to read and write the imports and exports of Wayfinding data. The VersionLog and WayfindingManifest were used in the past to support Google Drive, but aren't being used as of now, but we may need them in the future.
